## Understanding (restated)

Phone = second console with decision parity. TWO CONTOURS (INFO-033 final):
dialogue — event-driven, instant, bidirectional (ack ≤1 min ALWAYS; gate/E1/
result/overdue sent the moment they occur by the side that produced them via
ONE shared send helper; NARRATIVE beats ride it per profile level — open
detail, CEO may strike); digest — strictly scheduled (profile time ±5 min
daily, «сделано / в работе / ждёт тебя сегодня / расход» + 3-line changelog on
new release tag; already-signaled events = status lines, never duplicate
alarms). Physics: launchd polling listener (getUpdates), NO ports, NO
webhooks, NO resident LLM daemons — the listener is a plain script that acks
itself, persists the event to decisions/inbox/ (atomic tmp+rename), and wakes
the handler (the only place an LLM lives). File bus + closed-session pickup
remain the safety net. Security v1: chat_id binding (foreign → ignore + flag +
quarantine); risk-level HUMAN-TASK = explicit typed word, no buttons. NOT-DOING
(proposing = defect): 2FA, groups, inline editing, media. Mandated DoD
scenario: press with NO session running → persisted → consumed exactly once on
wake — proven by harness. Token: file path only; test token likewise a file;
BotFather registration needs a human Telegram account → build everything
against the stub, leave a one-line HUMAN-TASK for the CEO (Rowan: no E1).

## HARNESS-CHECKLIST (INFO-025) — 9 answers, before building

1. State-файл и резюмируемость: state lives in runtime/claude/telegram/state/
   (offset file for getUpdates — survives restarts, no replayed presses, H3;
   router pending-clarification files; narrative per-file offsets; signaled
   registry; quiet queue). decisions/inbox/ carries the durable events and
   promises (H13: pending-promise recorded in inbox so restart cannot drop
   it). Everything resumes from files; nothing lives only in a process.
2. Идемпотентность: listener pass is check→do (offset guards re-delivery);
   pickup consumes by atomic mv to done/ — second run is a no-op (H2 exactly
   once); digest guarded by a sent-today marker; install.sh re-run = health
   check (kit pattern).
3. Лимит автопопыток: send helper retries a failed API call max 2, then
   queues the event to state/queue/ and logs a concrete human line (check
   network / token file at <path>); never infinite.
4. Редакция секретов: token read from file path only, held in a local var,
   never echoed; curl URL never logged raw (log line shows bot<masked>);
   negative grep over listener log, state, inbox, harness transcripts = 0
